===============================================================================
 CS418 University of Illinois MP3
 Steven Kabbes :: skabbes2
===============================================================================
This mp showcases environment mapping and texture mapping onto a teapot.

Particularly, this implementation relies heavily on shaders to implement Phong
lighting, and sphere environment mapping.

To run the code, simply type make followed by ./mp3.

===============================================================================
 Special Features
===============================================================================
Press 'n' to toggle viewing normals
Press 't' to show only texture mapping
Press 'e' to show only environment mapping
Press 'm' to show a mixed texture and environment map filtered through a mask
